high_descs: Walk over to the tv and stand so you are on the left side of it looking down the length of the tv with the stand in front of you and the wall to your left.
Pick up the red credit card on the bottom shelf of the tv stand.
Turn right and walk to the coffee table then turn right and walk to the chair.
Set the credit card on the chair's cushion near the edge facing you.
Go back over to the tv stand.
Get the red credit card that's on the tv stand to the left of the tv.
Walk back over to where you put the first credit card.
Put this credit card directly to the left of the first credit card so they are touching and lined up.
anns.task_desc: Put two credit cards on the chair.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the black dresser.
Pick up the red credit card from the open shelf of the dresser.
Turn right and face the black chair on the right.
Put the credit card on the seat of the chair.
Turn right and go over to the dresser.
Pick up the credit card from on top of the dresser.
Turn around and go to face the black chair on the right.
Place the credit card down to the left of the first credit card.
anns.task_desc: Place the two credit cards from the dresser onto the seat of the chair on the right.

high_descs: Move to the black TV stand behind you
Pick up the credit card from the stand
Move to the first black chair on your right
Place the card on the chair
Move back to the black TV stand on the right
Pick up the second credit card from the stand.
Move back the to first black chair behind you
Place the second card next to the first on the chair
anns.task_desc: Put the two credit cards from the TV stand on the first black chair.
